You can now use solc 0.5.0 with dapptools by @dapphub!

Download instructions at https://dapp.tools  then:

dapp pkg selfupdate

dapp --use solc:0.5.0 build

First use will take a while, since it'll download/compile solc 0.5.0, next time it'll be fast! Thanks #solidity team!

931563972683358209.text:
Long-time Mozillian here. Nobody expected this exact outcome. From the inside it looks almost like luck—but it wasn't. The lessons I see are:
- invest $$$$ in R&D a decade before you need it
- hire PhDs
- take on long-shot projects in parallel
- retain your engineers

931565166063439872.text:
- invest in dev tools & infrastructure
- your product is MUCH better when your prioritize correctly
Rust was not the only important piece. Improvements in profiling (perf measurement) played an equally important role.
